summary:
•	Booking.com, Local Partner Services and Go-to-market tracks:
Full ownership of Targets Setting and Insights tools though, design, development&support through the lifecycle
	Vue.js, React.js frontend, Perl&Java Kubernetes backend, MySQL and ElasticSearch storage; Kubernetes +Shipper redundant multicluster architecture

•	Amazon Business Guided Buying, Policy Authoring team:
End-to-end ownership of restricted&blocked policy management. Policy evaluation using Amazon internal classification and industry standard UNSPSC
Design, development and support from UI widget to backend service to database to highly scalable policy evaluator
React+Redux frontend, Java service-oriented architecture backend, NoSQL database in AWS; serverless processing with AWS Lambdas and Step Functions, Elastic MapReduce filter precomputation with Apache Spark

•	PSTN Signaling & Media team at Skype:
Design, development, maintenance and support of world-class communication gateway software enabling full-scale interoperability between SIP/(S)RTP and Skype proprietary protocols
C++ on Linux mulitserver architecture; redundant &fault-tolerant components; full signaling stack and media handling
Next-gen converged cloud calling infrastructure underpinning future Teams PSTN calling capabilities. Geo-distributed and fault-tolerant design using ServiceFabric
Skype SMS cloud service: distributed fault tolerant C# cloud service in Azure
PSTN conference quality check and reporting system for Skype for Business. Distributed fault tolerant C# cloud service in Azure Linux media servers

•	In-house scientific software development for numerical calculations:
FORTRAN, Object Pascal, C++: numerical solutions, stochastic simulation, scaling behavior control, discrete simulations, phase space sampling
C++ discrete nucleation simulations: multicore support with OpenMP, automatic auxiliary numerical parameter tuning, precision control, numerical error control
